{"tid":1790356,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［Repost］#50Cents4HSBC 好可能係下一個風靡全港嘅 Challenge!","createTime":"2019-12-20T02:31:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T03:02:37.000Z","uid":236171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d2628d947e4000c534bf28b58aa916b9a3615260","tid":1790356,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T02:31:37.000Z","msg":"匯豐面臨國際制裁，又發現原來會隨時凍結人 Account. 咁危險梗係早走早着啦！！<br />\n<br />\n為咗提高大家安全存款嘅意識，有匯豐 Account 嘅不如一齊參加呢個 challenge<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>步驟：</strong><br />\n<br />\n1. 從 HSBC <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">ATM/櫃檯</span></strong>提走所有現金<br />\n2. 留低 $0.5 喺匯豐 Account<br />\n3. 影低帳號餘額<br />\n4. 喺 twitter/fb/ig 跟下面個 post 打一次<br />\n5. Hashtag #50Cents4HSBC<br />\n6. Tag 5 個朋友叫佢哋一齊做<br />\n<br />\n無匯豐 Account嘅唔使灰心，share/retweet下面個 tweet, 順便呢度幫手推下 post 都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/pentanov/status/1207692414531424258?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fpentanov%2Fstatus%2F1207692414531424258%3Fs%3D19&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5XNo2vAooDXMO4YLrfRUzdI%3D&h=8c654199\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fpentanov%2Fstatus%2F1207692414531424258%3Fs%3D19&h=e750bcc5\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/pentanov/status/1207692414531424258?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kyz8vhx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkyz8vhx.png&h=e92ae1e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d112ca081e78e7f77627b825bb450188d9054627","tid":1790356,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T02:43:50.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">FAQ</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>點解唔 cut account 要留$0.5俾匯豐？</strong><br />\n1. 剩返個少少錢嘅帳會增加匯豐行政成本。<br />\n2. 象徵意義，留返5毛勉勵佢為赤納粹賣命<br />\n<br />\n<strong>餘額太少會唔會俾銀行扣錢？</strong><br />\n1. 據我所知，匯豐已經取消咗Advance 或以下帳戶嘅最低存款要求。<br />\n2. 如果你唔清楚你個帳戶最低存款要求嘅，咪打電話去問下囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>點解 ATM/Over the counter? 網上匯款唔得？</strong><br />\n1. 因為銀行要keep 最低現金存款比率 RRR。<br />\n2. 如果 ATM/OTC 可以直接攞 cash, 而網上交易只係改變網上個數字。<br />\n3. 銀行當晚唔過 RRR 要問同行借錢，過夜息比一般貸款更高 <br />\n4. 所以嘔真金白銀出嚟會令銀行好頭痕。"},{"pid":"c6960b0431c27673be80191204149406af66843b","tid":1790356,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T02:45:32.000Z","msg":"記住遮住自己個 Account Number!!!!!!!<br />\n唔好玩自爆呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56dfd0a10f086562567c430d08ac452fa0834cc9","tid":1790356,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T02:46:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e53bd3c5872a276ebdeda647cffe0d6be106cd36","tid":1790356,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T02:48:30.000Z","msg":"說好的封一賠百呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a167ed97344e975c40de55bfee486887fba93399","tid":1790356,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T02:49:20.000Z","msg":"係咪開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de3c2e65b79cf936bd5ce9ac01270b2118d01965","tid":1790356,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T02:49:39.000Z","msg":"香港金總就極權無理打壓抗爭支援之譴責聲明<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1790265\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1790265</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d0b049755e0b9e5d2c58b5f3784827f3b597d657","tid":1790356,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T02:57:49.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">喺隔離台重開咗<br />\n呢個有得佢沉</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n[幫手推!!] 我正式宣